name: Martin John Callanan is okay
description:
Since 4 August 2007, all of Martin John Callanan's social media updates have read: "Martin John Callanan is okay". These are synced and aggregated at http://okay.greyisgood.eu

For this new generative version, minted 26 August 2021, the artwork automatically assigned the current time and date for when the artwork is viewed. This saves a lot of work, but probably renders the sentence untrue.
